<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="65" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph blockId="6.[145,760,1498,1551]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">
<typeStatus box="[145,199,1499,1520]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">Type</typeStatus>
species by subsequent designation (
<bibRefCitation author="Barker GM" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" pagination="38" refId="ref9307" refString="Barker GM. 1999. Naturalised terrestrial Stylommatophora (Mollusca: Gastropoda). In: Duval CT, ed. Fauna of New Zealand, no. 38. Lincoln: Manaaki Whenua Press." type="book chapter" year="1999">Barker, 1999: 62</bibRefCitation>
):
</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="De Cristofori &amp; Jan, 1832" authorityName="De Cristofori &amp; Jan" authorityYear="1832" box="[200,674,1529,1551]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="mazzullii">
<emphasis box="[200,374,1529,1550]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">Helix mazzullii</emphasis>
De Cristofori &amp; Jan, 1832
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[145,762,1591,1889]" lastBlockId="6.[809,1426,1063,1269]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis box="[145,253,1591,1612]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">Remarks:</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Colomba MS &amp; Gregorini A &amp; Liberto F &amp; Reitano A &amp; Giglio S &amp; Sparacio I" box="[274,521,1591,1614]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" pagination="1 - 42" refId="ref9678" refString="Colomba MS, Gregorini A, Liberto F, Reitano A, Giglio S, Sparacio I. 2011. Monographic revision of the endemic Helix mazzullii De Cristofori &amp; Jan, 1832 complex from Sicily and re-introduction of the genus Erctella Monterosato, 1894 (Pulmonata, Stylommatophora, Helicidae). Zootaxa 3134: 1 - 42." type="journal article" year="2011">
Colomba 
<emphasis box="[383,440,1591,1613]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">et al.</emphasis>
(2011)
</bibRefCitation>
stated that the 
<typeStatus box="[711,761,1592,1613]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Monterosato" authorityYear="1894" box="[267,361,1622,1643]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Cornu" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="60" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Erctella">
<emphasis box="[267,361,1622,1643]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">Erctella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was designated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Pilsbry HA" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" pagination="161 - 336" refId="ref11142" refString="Pilsbry HA. 1895. Guide to the study of helices. In: Pilsbry HA, ed. Manual of conchology; structural and systematic. With illustrations of the species. Second Series: Pulmonata, Vol. 9, Part 36. Philadelphia: Academy of Natural Sciences, 161 - 336, pls 41 - 71, frontispiece." type="book chapter" year="1895">Pilsbry (1895: 316)</bibRefCitation>
. However, 
<bibRefCitation author="Pilsbry HA" box="[333,503,1653,1675]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" pagination="161 - 336" refId="ref11142" refString="Pilsbry HA. 1895. Guide to the study of helices. In: Pilsbry HA, ed. Manual of conchology; structural and systematic. With illustrations of the species. Second Series: Pulmonata, Vol. 9, Part 36. Philadelphia: Academy of Natural Sciences, 161 - 336, pls 41 - 71, frontispiece." type="book chapter" year="1895">Pilsbry (1895)</bibRefCitation>
only mentioned that 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Monterosato" authorityYear="1894" box="[145,236,1683,1704]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Cornu" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="60" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Erctella">
<emphasis box="[145,236,1683,1704]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">Erctella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was established ‘for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="De Cristofori &amp; Jan" authorityYear="1832" box="[476,618,1683,1705]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="mazzullii">
<emphasis box="[476,618,1683,1705]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">H. mazzullii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
’ and missed that 
<bibRefCitation author="Monterosato T" box="[206,446,1714,1736]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" pagination="165 - 173" refId="ref10656" refString="Monterosato T. di Maria di 1894. Conchiglie terrestri viventi e fossili di Monte Pellegrino. Il Naturalista Siciliano 13: 165 - 173." type="journal article" year="1894">Monterosato (1894)</bibRefCitation>
included 
<taxonomicName authority="Benoit, 1857" authorityName="Benoit" authorityYear="1857" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="costae" subGenus="Erctella">
<emphasis box="[571,635,1714,1735]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">Helix</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[655,752,1714,1735]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">Erctella</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[145,217,1746,1767]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">costae</emphasis>
Benoit, 1857
</taxonomicName>
as a second nominal species in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Monterosato" authorityYear="1894" box="[145,239,1775,1796]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Cornu" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="60" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Erctella">
<emphasis box="[145,239,1775,1796]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">Erctella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
or considered this unimportant because he included 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Benoit" authorityYear="1857" box="[246,345,1807,1828]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="costae">
<emphasis box="[246,345,1807,1828]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">H. costae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the synonymy of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="De Cristofori &amp; Jan" authorityYear="1832" box="[563,701,1806,1828]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="mazzullii">
<emphasis box="[563,701,1806,1828]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">H. mazzullii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This does not constitute a valid 
<typeStatus box="[470,521,1837,1858]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">type</typeStatus>
species designation (see also: 
<bibRefCitation author="Welter-Schultes FW" box="[268,539,1867,1889]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" refId="ref11906" refString="Welter-Schultes FW. 2012. European non-marine molluscs, a guide for species identification. Gottingen: Planet Poster Editions." type="book" year="2012">Welter-Schultes, 2012</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Welter-Schultes FW" box="[565,883,1063,1889]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" refId="ref11906" refString="Welter-Schultes FW. 2012. European non-marine molluscs, a guide for species identification. Gottingen: Planet Poster Editions." type="book" year="2012">Welter-Schultes (2012)</bibRefCitation>
suggested that 
<bibRefCitation author="Schileyko AA" box="[1073,1269,1063,1085]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" pagination="1765 - 1906" refId="ref11534" refString="Schileyko AA. 2006. Treatise on recent terrestrial pulmonate molluscs. Part 13. Helicidae, Pleurodontidae, Polygyridae, Ammonitellidae, Oreohelicidae, Thysanophoridae. Ruthenica, Supplement 2: 1765 - 1906." type="journal article" year="2006">Schileyko (2006)</bibRefCitation>
was the first to designate the 
<typeStatus box="[1015,1067,1094,1115]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Monterosato" authorityYear="1894" box="[1203,1298,1094,1115]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Cornu" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="60" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Erctella">
<emphasis box="[1203,1298,1094,1115]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">Erctella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. However, this had already been done by 
<bibRefCitation author="Barker GM" box="[1169,1331,1124,1147]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" pagination="38" refId="ref9307" refString="Barker GM. 1999. Naturalised terrestrial Stylommatophora (Mollusca: Gastropoda). In: Duval CT, ed. Fauna of New Zealand, no. 38. Lincoln: Manaaki Whenua Press." type="book chapter" year="1999">Barker (1999)</bibRefCitation>
. It does not matter that 
<bibRefCitation author="Barker GM" box="[1005,1172,1155,1177]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" pagination="38" refId="ref9307" refString="Barker GM. 1999. Naturalised terrestrial Stylommatophora (Mollusca: Gastropoda). In: Duval CT, ed. Fauna of New Zealand, no. 38. Lincoln: Manaaki Whenua Press." type="book chapter" year="1999">Barker (1999)</bibRefCitation>
erroneously thought that 
<taxonomicName authorityName="De Cristofori &amp; Jan" authorityYear="1832" box="[869,1018,1186,1207]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="mazzullii">
<emphasis box="[869,1018,1186,1207]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">H. mazzullii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the 
<typeStatus box="[1106,1158,1186,1207]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Monterosato" authorityYear="1894" box="[1292,1387,1186,1207]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Cornu" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="6" pageNumber="60" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Erctella">
<emphasis box="[1292,1387,1186,1207]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="65">Erctella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by monotypy [as 
<bibRefCitation author="Schileyko AA" box="[975,1170,1216,1238]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" pagination="1765 - 1906" refId="ref11534" refString="Schileyko AA. 2006. Treatise on recent terrestrial pulmonate molluscs. Part 13. Helicidae, Pleurodontidae, Polygyridae, Ammonitellidae, Oreohelicidae, Thysanophoridae. Ruthenica, Supplement 2: 1765 - 1906." type="journal article" year="2006">Schileyko (2006)</bibRefCitation>
also did; 
<bibRefCitation author="ICZN &amp; International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" box="[1284,1418,1217,1238]" pageId="6" pageNumber="65" refId="ref10311" refString="ICZN (International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature). 1999. International code of zoological nomenclature, 4 th edn. London: International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature." type="book" year="1999">ICZN, 1999</bibRefCitation>
: Article 69.1.1].
</paragraph>
